Some people wear suits when they are going to the office or some special occasions.
And for others – especially secret police and other security agents like them – the suit is like a uniform.
Just like them, 24-year-old Zubairu Suleiman dons the suit – complete with shirtsleeve and necktie – when going out for business – hawking kolanut.
In this video, he explains the rationale behind his choice of fashion.